COMMS: FLASH TRAFFIC — COMSUBLANT TO USS JACKSONVILLE.
COMMS: Akula-class submarine confirmed operating in your patrol sector. Designated Sierra One.
INTEL: Acoustic intelligence suggests this is K-157 Vepr. One of their quieter boats. Last detection was thirty-six hours ago — nothing since.
COMMS: You are weapons free. Locate and neutralize Sierra One.
COMMS: Reminder: this is submarine-versus-submarine. Noise discipline is everything. Above six knots, you are the one being hunted.
COMMS: COMMS out.
